                        <title type="desc" key="work_13355">Noted Missal, Use of York</title>
                       
                        <note>On the front fly leaf: portions of the marriage service and the ritual of the Extreme Unction. At the end of the volume: portions of the commons of a virgin and martyr, of a virgin not martyr, of a holy woman and of more virgins; common of the Dedication, some votive masses.</note>
